==Iderman==

===At Wejɛud (At Wejaoud)===

At Wejɛud d adrum ameqran n taddart yesɛa azal n carit (30) ye xxamen, adrum-agi yebḍa ɣef krad (3) nneqmat (nom de famille) deg tira Tafransist gar-asen '''Adjed''', '''Djaouani''' akk d '''Djaou'''.

ass-agi tawacult '''Adjed''' d nutni id yegran aṭṭas deg we drum acku tawacult '''Djaou''' udren akk ɣer [[Taddart: Taqriett|Tqeriett]] ma d '''Djaouani''' akk d '''Adjed''' aṭṭas daɣen ig udren ɣer [[Taddart: Taqriett|Tqeriett]], dacu aṭṭas ig qqimen deg taddart.

